CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 10, 1956, pg. 26, reads: "Farewell to Si - Tabbed everybody's All-American and labeled by coach Dudley Moore as the greatest basketball player he has ever seen, Sihugo Green ended his home career, scoring 29 points and leading the Dukes to a 64-56 win over St. Bonaventure at the Gardens Monday... - Harris photos."
TitMainTitle: Duquesne University basketball player Sihugo "Si" Green, seated on bench in locker room, in Duquesne Gardens
